Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.30,0:01:05.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency. Level 1 alert.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.40,0:01:07.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,Omega 1 is rebooting.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.45,0:01:10.55,Normal,,0,0,0,,Alpha 1 has begun reassembling its genomes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:13.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,It's been confirmed: exon replacement is occurring!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.35,0:01:17.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,Nucleotide bases reaching 850 million...1.2 billion! It's way too fast!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.00,0:01:20.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,Confirmed! Alpha 1 has accessed the Raziel mainframe!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.05,Normal,,0,0,0,,Fake-Net deployed! Alpha 1 evaded!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.10,Normal,,0,0,0,,Activating emergency shields... We're locked out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.50,0:01:31.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,It's corrupting the entire matrix... Captain!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.60,0:01:33.35,Normal,,0,0,0,,Cut the cables manually!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.35,0:01:36.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,Roger! Initiating cable explosives...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ejection confirmed!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.40,0:01:43.25,Normal,,0,0,0,,...No! No effect!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.45,Normal,,0,0,0,,Omega 1 still progressing! It won't stop!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.25,0:01:50.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,It's taken control of 98% of our weapons!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.80,Normal,,0,0,0,,It's communicating with the Faust navigation system at an incredible speed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.75,Normal,,0,0,0,,Phase-space logic is being overridden!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.40,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ergosphere is expanding,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.35,0:01:59.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,and a plane is forming within the core!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.20,Normal,,0,0,0,,We're switching to space warp mode!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.30,0:02:05.10,Normal,,0,0,0,,Alpha 1 is transmitting new coordinates to Faust!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.20,0:02:09.05,Normal,,0,0,0,,The coordinates entered were NZ128, EZ061...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.30,Normal,,0,0,0,,...Lost Jerusalem!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.90,Normal,,0,0,0,,At this rate...the damn thing is sure to invade...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,Engine Room!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.80,Normal,,0,0,0,,Insert the emergency break plug!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.10,Normal,,0,0,0,,...Engine Room?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.45,0:02:19.95,Normal,,0,0,0,,Engin--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.35,0:02:31.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.85,0:02:41.60,Normal,,0,0,0,,All civilians and crew members, evacuate now to the escape shuttles.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.30,Normal,,0,0,0,,Launch in sequence following complete evacuation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.80,Normal,,0,0,0,,We hereby abandon this ship.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,...All of you...leave now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,An evacuation order has been issued.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,The ship will be abandoned.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.70,0:03:00.75,Normal,,0,0,0,,All crew members, quickly proceed to shuttle boarding gates. Repeat--
